`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
Tone.js `Volume` takes dB values (not 0–1 scalars like raw Web Audio). The `toDestination()` call chains the node to Tone's master output. The Panner3D pool is a classic resource-pool pattern: fixed-size allocation at init, acquire/release without re-construction — avoids the expensive AudioContext node creation on each sound event.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
